# Part 2: Looking at the data

A couple of interesting things can be gleaned from the data. One is the ffact that China is not entirely comprised of provinces. There are 4 cities within the dataset that comprise China's municipalities: Beijin, Tianjin, Shanghai, Chongqing. These municipalities both hold the rank of both city and provinces themselves.
